data.description: WINDING WALK GEM!  Welcome to your dream home located in the highly sought-after community of Winding Walk in Otay Ranch! This corner-unit property has everything that you been looking for with 2,375 square feet of living space, 4 spacious bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, open floor plan with lots of natural light, high ceilings, 2 fireplaces, large loft, private side yard, large two car garage and plenty of upgrades.  This gorgeous home features a range of premium amenities to include solar panels, recess lights throughout the home, lots of smart home features, and custom built in storage.  The gourmet kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, lots of cabinetry and a large island.  Located on the first floor is one full bedroom and bathroom with direct access to the two-car garage.  There is also the formal living room which could also be an optional 5th bedroom.  The upper level of the home offers 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, a dedicated laundry room, and a large loft. Enjoy summer days at the community pool and spa located right across the street.  Hurry, this one will not last!
